<Turn speaker="spk1" startTime="1045.569" endTime="1106.53" fidelity="high">
<Sync time="1045.569"/>
Karkoli nam bo 
<Sync time="1047.131"/>
prihodnost prinesla, in to so dejansko razmere nepredvidljive, 
<Sync time="1052.024"/>
